9 in D Minor (Sir Georg Solti cond. Chicago Symphony Orchestra;
Solos), John Pellowe, engineer; Faure: Requiem, Op. 48@Durufle:
Requiem, Op. 9 (Robert Shaw cond. Atlanta Symphony Orchestra &
Chorus; Solos), Jack Renner, engineer; Hindemith: When Lilacs Last
in the Dooryard Bloom'd (A Requeim for Those We Love) (Robert Shaw
