engineer; Tchaikovsky: 1812 Overture@Romeo & Juliet@The Nutcracker
Suite (Sir Georg Solti cond. Chicago Symphony Orchestra), John
Pellowe, Engineer.
   _ CLASSICAL PRODUCER OF THE YEAR: Steven Epstein; Thomas Frost;
Michael Haas; Jay David Saks; Robert Woods.
